    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è To change the border color on hover in mui textfield, you have to use mui material styles, which we can define on hover‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! ‚ù§Ô∏è</p>\n<p>To change the border color on hover in mui textfield, you have to use mui material styles, which we can define on hover in mui textfield.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you. how to change mui textfield border color on hover in react js mui text field.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> CssTextField <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">styled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>TextField<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'&amp; .MuiOutlinedInput-root'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">'&amp;:hover fieldset'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">borderColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'yellow'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Install the following packages to use mui text field in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npm install @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">yarn add @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<h2>MUI material text field change border color on hover example</h2>\n<p>To change the border color on hover, the class <code class=\"language-text\">.&amp; .MuiOutlinedInput-root</code> has to be used.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> styled <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material/styles'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Box <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material/Box'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> TextField <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material/TextField'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> CssTextField <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">styled</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>TextField<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'&amp; label.Mui-focused'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">color</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'green'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'&amp; .MuiInput-underline:after'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">borderBottomColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'green'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string-property property\">'&amp; .MuiOutlinedInput-root'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">'&amp; fieldset'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">borderColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'red'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">'&amp;:hover fieldset'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">borderColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'yellow'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string-property property\">'&amp;.Mui-focused fieldset'</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">borderColor</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'green'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">CustomizedInputs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Box\n      component<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"form\"</span>\n      noValidate\n      sx<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">display</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'grid'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">gridTemplateColumns</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">sm</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'1fr 1fr'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">gap</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>CssTextField label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Custom CSS\"</span> id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"custom-css-outlined-input\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Box<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">@mui/material</code> TextField component and changed the border color on the hover of all types of MUI Textfield.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b4d75c5c99ef4a672ef447cb6df5e08f/38f6f/border-color-on-hover.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.26582278481012%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, Mui Textfield Border Color on Hover\"\n        title=\"React, Mui Textfield Border Color on Hover\"\n        src=\"/static/b4d75c5c99ef4a672ef447cb6df5e08f/828fb/border-color-on-hover.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b4d75c5c99ef4a672ef447cb6df5e08f/ff44c/border-color-on-hover.jpg 158w,\n/static/b4d75c5c99ef4a672ef447cb6df5e08f/a6688/border-color-on-hover.jpg 315w,\n/static/b4d75c5c99ef4a672ef447cb6df5e08f/828fb/border-color-on-hover.jpg 630w,\n/static/b4d75c5c99ef4a672ef447cb6df5e08f/0ede0/border-color-on-hover.jpg 945w,\n/static/b4d75c5c99ef4a672ef447cb6df5e08f/3ac88/border-color-on-hover.jpg 1260w,\n/static/b4d75c5c99ef4a672ef447cb6df5e08f/38f6f/border-color-on-hover.jpg 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best üëç\nü§ù</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to change mui textfield border color on hover in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"November 09, 2022","description":"Example of change mui textfield border color on hover in React js with step by step tutorial - aGuideHub","social_image":"media/template/reactjs.jpg"}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to change mui textfield font size in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022-11-10-how-to-change-mui-textfield-font-size-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to change mui textfield border radius in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022-11-08-how-to-change-mui-textfield-border-radius-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2022-11-09-how-to-change-mui-textfield-border-color-on-hover-in-react-js/","prevSlug":"/blog/2022-11-10-how-to-change-mui-textfield-font-size-in-react-js/","nextSlug":"/blog/2022-11-08-how-to-change-mui-textfield-border-radius-in-react-js/"}},
